Jorgie Porter has been soaking up the sun while on holiday with her fiance Ollie Piotrowski, who proposed to her in December. The 34-year-old is enjoying a break in the luxury Cayo resort in Elounda, Crete. The on-screen star opted to go topless as she went for a dip in the swimming pool. The actress cupped her cleavage area in the private pool on holiday as she went makeup-free. In view of her 703,000 followers, she captioned the post: "Perks of a private pool." Fans gushed over the racy photo, as Kieran commented: "You look absolutely stunning as always." Kev agreed: "Smoking hot," while Jenny added: "Wow." Jorgie is famous for playing Theresa McQueen in Hollyoaks from 2008 until 2016 and again from 2020. She also appeared in the I'm A Celeb jungle as well as Dancing on Ice and Celebrity First Dates.